# Task List: Migration to Acordeon-Carrossel Pattern

[ ] Map all `ContentAccordion` components in the target lesson files.
[ ] Analyze the internal slides of each `ContentAccordion` to identify logical splits (e.g., Concepts vs. Examples, Rules vs. Exceptions).
[ ] Split single `ContentAccordion` blocks into multiple independent `ContentAccordion` components per module (e.g., Acordeon 1, Acordeon 2).
[ ] Update typography within all Accordion slides: increase font sizes (e.g., change `text-sm` to `text-base` and `text-xs` to `text-sm` or remove them to use defaults).
[ ] Verify visual layout and test responsiveness to ensure no content is squeezed.
[ ] Repeat for all modules in the targeted file(s).
